@DATABASE "Oriental Hero"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - O - Oriental Hero"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - O
                   ====================================

                               Oriental Hero
                               =============



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Energy" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(28995,0)"}         28995,0
@{"Energy = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPOKE(27472,255)"}         27472,x (x= 1-255)


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
